# Crontab file for system-specific jobs - executes on every webserver
#
# There should be no entries here, except system maintenance tasks (like indexers)
# Please use Jenkins to manage other jobs.
#
# This file contains the crontab file which will be updated while deployment
# Following variables are available:
# ENVIRONMENT (z.B: production)
# CURRENT_DIR (z.B: /data/shop/production/current)
#
# SEE: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cron

* * * * * www-data cd ${CURRENT_DIR}/deploy && flock -n /tmp/lock.${APPLICATION_ENV}.memcache ./exec_foreach_store ./cron_update_memcache
# * * * * * www-data cd ${CURRENT_DIR}/deploy && flock -n /tmp/lock.${APPLICATION_ENV}.monitor_fatals ./exec_default_store ./cron_monitor_fatals
